{"tid":1808819,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人應該要對自己講嘅廣東話而感到驕傲","createTime":"2020-01-02T15:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T08:56:58.000Z","uid":64694,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f92b4c15bd667b1ab3b3d6e92bebc1af8a6059d6","tid":1808819,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇到一篇文，講法國人唔會輕易講英文，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">法國人對於自己的語言十分驕傲</span>，篇文寫話「法國人不喜歡外國人在法國還要說英文，法國人對自己的語言很驕傲，覺得在法國就應該說法文，劈頭就用英文問話，會讓某些守舊的人火大」<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得我哋都要學似法國人咁，為我哋自己嘅本土語言、我哋嘅廣東話母語而感到驕傲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次遇到人問路，我哋一定要佢哋用廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果佢哋用普通話問路，即係唔尊重我哋香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n篇文叫「【其他】 法國旅遊英文行得通嗎？<br />\n<br />\n」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=1931538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D1931538&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPsljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=ea3c4c61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=1931538</a>"},{"pid":"46b362085d9077bf20c91c9b1e7a13be5b2bbe7e","tid":1808819,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"619bc81fd4556715940cce38ca1356345e26889d","tid":1808819,"uid":5995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都要學廣東話"},{"pid":"d26f27cb0692ca286367f6b56f1eae393d422d41","tid":1808819,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"「但有一次我問英國朋友他對法國人看法，他就說在法國時說英文，法國人不理會他」<br />\n<br />\n可以改成<br />\n<br />\n「但有一次我問大陸朋友他對香港人看法，他就說在香港時說普通話，香港人不理會他」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bf839293de1fef455853f1115a82c4b8d8f9e3","tid":1808819,"uid":103521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"我已經戒左，只要有支那遊客問我都會叫佢用廣東話，唔識叫佢查，想搵其他人我會跟撚住佢，叫人唔好幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5007af254c128eb49f1afed1eb452984a13f136c","tid":1808819,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27bf839293de1fef455853f1115a82c4b8d8f9e3","tid":1808819,"uid":103521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"我已經戒左，只要有支那遊客問我都會叫佢用廣東話，唔識叫佢查，想搵其他人我會跟撚住佢，叫人唔好幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"所以我哋除咗要對廣東話而自豪之外，重要好似傳教咁將之傳播開去，等多啲人學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a627333f3296c1cae7eceadfe4f77e98204d1836","tid":1808819,"uid":195493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3eb370a9d5232a5235a663d5388cd51bc9906fca","tid":1808819,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"個個國家都係咁架啦<br />\n係得香港唔係"},{"pid":"4de1247996835ce9a93affba9a6c44b0df06dc4a","tid":1808819,"uid":103521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5007af254c128eb49f1afed1eb452984a13f136c","tid":1808819,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27bf839293de1fef455853f1115a82c4b8d8f9e3","tid":1808819,"uid":103521,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"我已經戒左，只要有支那遊客問我都會叫佢用廣東話，唔識叫佢查，想搵其他人我會跟撚住佢，叫人唔好幫佢<img sr